.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-4::.
There 7 different types of food: lime, tomato, lemon, grapefruit, cherry, pumpkin, orange
1. the person eating lime is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
3. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating lime##1
6. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
7. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
8. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3     |    4     |   5    |     6      |  7   |
| Food   | lime | orange | grapefruit | pumpkin | cherry | lemon | tomato |

