.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-5::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, tram, airplane, trike, bus, ship, snowmobile
1. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3    |    4     |   5   |   6   |   7    |
| Transport   | tram | trike | bus | airplane | scooter | snowmobile | ship |

