.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, aconite, lily, marigold, dahlia, begonia
1. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
6. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
7. the person who growslily is on the far left##1
8. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2       |     3      |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7      |
| Flower   | lily | marigold | dahlia | daisy | aconite | zinnia | begonia |

