.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-7::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: trike, taxi, roller, bus, train, scooter, helicopter
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the bus is the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the scooter##2
6. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2    |    3     |  4  |   5   |    6     |   7    |
| Transport   | trike | bus | train | scooter | helicopter | roller | taxi |

