.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-9::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: blood-red, ebony, amber, red, apricot, lilac, light-blue
1. the person who likes red is the person who likes red##1
2. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
5. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person who likes lilac##3
6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
7. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
9. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |   2   |     3      |   4    |   5    |  6   |   7   |
| Color   | amber | light-blue | blood-red | apricot | lilac | ebony | red |

