.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-13::.
7 different games are played: backgammon, poker, billiard, monopoly, scrabble, whist, chess
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6  |  7  |
| Game   | poker | monopoly | scrabble | billiard | whist | chess | backgammon |

