.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-14::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, baccarat, alhambra, swisher, blend, ritmeester, aristoff
1. the blend-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
3. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
6. the dannemann-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
7. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2   |     3      |    4     |      5       |       6       |     7      |
| Cigar   | alhambra | blend | swisher | baccarat | ritmeester | aristoff | dannemann |

