4. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |     3     |   4    |    5    |  6  |  7   |
| Sport   | swimming | volleyball | basketball | parkour | sailing | baseball | lacrosse |

