.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: house, trance, salsa, hip-hop, folk, metal, funk
1. the fan of funk is on the right of the fan of folk##1
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the fan of folk is between the fan of funk and the fan of metal##2
4. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of house is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
7. the fan of salsa is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of trance is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |    4     |    5    |    6    |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | house | trance | metal | folk | funk | hip-hop | salsa |

