.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-4-20::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  manager, librarian, doctor, dressmaker, teacher, photographer, fisherman
 1. the teacher is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 2. the fisherman is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 3. the teacher is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 4. the teacher is in an odd position##4
 5. the manager is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 6. the teacher is on the left of the doctor##1
 7. the manager is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 8. the photographer is in an odd position##4
 9. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the teacher##3
10. the manager is on the left or right of the librarian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |  2   |  3   |  4   |     5      |     6     |  7   |
| Job   | librarian | manager | fisherman | dressmaker | teacher | doctor | photographer |

 